    slug: "brass-handle-rehal-7-inch",
    description: `This Brass Handle Rehal is a 7-inch wooden Quran stand crafted with fitted brass handles that add both structural reinforcement and visual distinction to the traditional rehal design. The rehal — also known as a rihal or xamadan — is the folding book rest used across the Muslim world to hold the Holy Quran open at a comfortable reading angle during recitation, study, and memorization. This particular model features a solid wood construction with a warm natural finish that highlights the grain of the timber, paired with brass-finished metal handles mounted on either side that serve as both carrying grips and folding mechanisms.

The 7-inch size refers to the folded dimensions of the stand, making it a compact and portable option that easily fits into a bag, backpack, or briefcase alongside other study materials. Despite its small folded footprint, the stand opens to provide a stable, angled surface that holds standard and medium-sized Quran editions securely in place. The brass handles are securely fastened to the wooden panels with screws or rivets, and their metal construction adds durability to the points where the rehal experiences the most stress during repeated folding and unfolding. The hinge mechanism allows the stand to open smoothly to the correct reading angle and fold flat for storage or transport, and the brass handles ensure that the user's fingers are not pinched during operation.

This rehal is suitable for use in homes, mosques, madrasahs, offices, and during travel. Students who attend Quran classes or hifz (memorization) programs find the 7-inch size convenient for carrying to and from their lessons. The brass-accented design also makes this rehal an attractive decorative piece for a bookshelf, mantelpiece, or side table when not in active use, as the contrast between the warm wood and the polished brass creates an appealing visual effect. The craftsmanship reflects the traditional woodworking techniques used in rehal production for generations, with smooth surfaces that will not scratch or damage delicate Quran pages. For anyone who reads the Quran regularly and needs a reliable, portable stand that combines practical functionality with a touch of elegance, this Brass Handle Rehal in the 7-inch size provides a dependable solution that balances compactness with adequate support for comfortable reading.`,
    metaDescription: "Brass Handle Rehal 7-inch is a portable wooden Quran stand with brass-finished handles. Compact folding design for home, mosque, and travel use."
